title: Holiday on the agenda for jaded Harris
text: Holiday on the agenda for jaded Harris Friday, 16 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) Bowling all-rounder James Harris has his sights set on the beach after ending a long season with Middlesex by completing the second Big Bike Ride to raise funds for the PCA Benevolent Fund and Tom Maynard Trust.
